      "content": "i tried the zyrtec like 10 mins ago but it doesn't seem to be doing much and the whistling is getting louder. i dont really want to go to the doctor if i can help it, it's such a hassle. can i just take a double dose of the zyrtec or maybe a different allergy pill to make it kick in faster? i just need to stop this wheezing so i can sleep",
